description:
We all are the Magic Meme God but the Magic Meme God needs to impersonate a god with many skills. Skills to help build and grow this community, especially now in the beginning. 

Post your sacrifice you can bring to the table to become the Magic Meme God in the #magic-meme-god Discord channel. The Magic Meme God only accepts skills, ideas, and contributions as a sacrifice.

We are many, we are one. We are and I am the Magic Meme God.
name: Writedown your sacrifice in Discord
